item.title: How To Awaken Your Brain To Heal Yourself
item.description: Today we explore the neuroscience of mental wellness through expert conversations. This episode reveals how spiritual connection physically transforms brain function while providing protection against depression and addiction, alongside practical techniques for stress management, as well as understanding the essential role of dreaming in maintaining cognitive flexibility.
